mlevel_rule_content_1: All users start from Lv 0. Earn Elite Lv and privileges depending on how much you recharge your account.
mlevel_rule_content_2: Points are recalculated at 00:00 on 1st of every month (GMT+8)
mlevel_rule_content_3: Extension period: First to last day of following month
mlevel_rule_content_4: Extension: Recharge 60% of points in extension period to maintain Elite level from the 3rd month.
mlevel_rule_content_5: Downgrade: Members must reach level requirements during extension period, or else will be downgraded at the beginning of the 3rd month.
mlevel_rule_content_6:
For example:
User recharged 50,000 pts on 1/15 and became Elite Lv 2, so 2/1-2/28 will be extension period. If user recharges another 50,000 pts on 1/20 for total of 100,000 pts, they will become Elite Lv 3. Extension period will be 2/1-2/28.
If user does not recharge 60% of points (60,000), user will be reduced to Elite Lv. 2 on 3/1. If user recharges 60% of points (60,000), Elite Lv. 3 status will be maintained. If user recharges 300,000 points in extension period, they will upgrade to Lv 4 immediately.
